for engagement rings due to its brilliance and durability, especially for those seeking a budget-friendly alternative. Its hardness of 9.25 makes it nearly as durable as a diamond, which has a hardness of 10.<\/p>"}},"text_FHPVxD":{"type":"text","settings":{"title":"Will moissanite test as a diamond?","heading_font_size":"heading-small","text":"<p>Moissanite can be detected as a diamond by standard diamond testers. However, more advanced equipment can easily distinguish between moissanite and diamonds.<\/p>"}},"text_bVMT7M":{"type":"text","settings":{"title":"Is moissanite hypoallergenic?","heading_font_size":"heading-small","text":"<p>Yes, moissanite is typically set in hypoallergenic metals like 925 sterling silver or other non-reactive metals, making it suitable for most people, even those with sensitive skin.<\/p>"}},"text_6g9fGt":{"type":"text","settings":{"title":"Have more questions?","heading_font_size":"heading-small","text":"<p>We’ve highlighted the 5 most common questions here, but if you have more, feel free to check out our full<a href=\"https:\/\/solariijewelry.com\/pages\/faq\" title=\"FAQ\"><em><strong>FAQ<\/strong><\/em><\/a>section for additional details.<\/p>"}}},"block_order":["faq-1","text_eMTErH","text_tCiypz","text_FHPVxD","text_bVMT7M","text_6g9fGt"],"settings":{"default_open":false,"title":"Moissanite Jewelry FAQ","heading_font_size":"heading-small","show_icon":false,"icon_name":"icon-fast-shipment","icon_size":20,"width":"wrapper","color_scheme":"scheme-1","icon_color":"#545454","padding_top":0,"padding_bottom":0}},"section_accordion_PCmrb3":{"type":"section-accordion","blocks":{"icon_yFJEGT":{"type":"icon","settings":{"icon_name":"icon-green-shipment","icon_size":20,"icon_color":"","title":"Free shipping & Free package gifts","heading_font_size":"heading-small","icon_alignment":"left","text":"<p>We do our best to process and ship your order as soon as we can! Below you'll find our shipping options and their estimated shipping times.<br\/><br\/>• Free Shipping - (6-12 Business Days)<br\/>• Express Shipping - (5-8 Business Days)<br\/>• Rush Shipping - (3-5 Business Days)<\/p><p><a href=\"\/policies\/shipping-policy\" title=\"Shipping Policy\"><strong>Learn More<\/strong><\/a><\/p>","text_alignment":"text-left"}},"icon_63XwYw":{"type":"icon","settings":{"icon_name":"icon-location","icon_size":20,"icon_color":"","title":"Order tracking","heading_font_size":"heading-small","icon_alignment":"left","text":"<p>Tracking numbers are automatically sent once your order has been shipped. Please check your junk folder if you do not receive one 72 hours after placing your order.<\/p>","text_alignment":"text-left"}},"icon_GQYUR9":{"type":"icon","settings":{"icon_name":"icon-chat","icon_size":20,"icon_color":"","title":"Contact Us","heading_font_size":"heading-small","icon_alignment":"left","text":"<p><strong>If you have any questions about your order, please reach out to us at <\/strong><a><strong>service@solariijewelry.com<\/strong><\/a><strong>. We typically respond within 24 hours.<\/strong><\/p>","text_alignment":"text-left"}}},"block_order":["icon_yFJEGT","icon_63XwYw","icon_GQYUR9"],"settings":{"default_open":false,"title":"Shipping & Returns","heading_font_size":"heading-small","show_icon":false,"icon_name":"icon-shield","icon_size":20,"width":"wrapper","color_scheme":"scheme-1","icon_color":"#545454","padding_top":0,"padding_bottom":0}},"about":{"type":"section-accordion","blocks":{"text_XPN9xJ":{"type":"text","settings":{"title":"100% Handcrafted, No Matter the Order Size","heading_font_size":"heading-small","text":"<p>We promise that every piece—regardless of price or quantity—is carefully handcrafted by our skilled artisans with the highest level of craftsmanship.<\/p>"}},"text_8yRyEy":{"type":"text","settings":{"title":"What You See Is Exactly What You Get","heading_font_size":"heading-small","text":"<p>We guarantee our videos and images match the real product. No exaggeration, no surprises.<\/p>"}},"tex