ing the same authenticity and quality as diamonds at a fraction of the cost.<\/p>","text_font_size":"body-medium","button_text":"","button_url":"","button_type":"btn--primary","button_size":"","button_style":"btn--solid","show_arrow":false,"image_aspect_ratio":1,"mobile_image_aspect_ratio":0.8,"heading_tag":"automatic"}}},"block_order":["image_dPJDhE","image_xPcwdG","image_AiFaA9"],"settings":{"title":"","heading_font_size":"heading-medium","align_heading":"text-left","align_text":"text-left","width":"wrapper--full-padded","align_columns":"flex-align-top","layout":"grid","grid":3,"layout_mobile":"1","color_scheme":"scheme-1","padding_top":15,"padding_bottom":50,"heading_tag":"automatic"}},"section_rich_text_mYtcWE":{"type":"section-rich-text","blocks":{"heading_tCRrAk":{"type":"heading","settings":{"title":"What You Recieve","heading_font_size":"heading-medium","padding_bottom":6,"heading_tag":"automatic"}}},"block_order":["heading_tCRrAk"],"name":"Rich text","settings":{"align_text":"text-center","width":"wrapper","color_scheme":"scheme-a99bb364-57b9-4cca-912d-b0f18794ffaf","overlay_type":"disabled","padding_top":14,"padding_bottom":0}},"section_columns_8ejR6x":{"type":"section-columns","blocks":{"image_nU7PXt":{"type":"image","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/1_e3d88236-5dfb-47f1-b62f-9094f7c755ff.webp","image_width":100,"image_shape":"normal","title":"Exquisite Packaging","heading_font_size":"heading-medium","text":"<p>Receiving your bespoke piece from SolariiJewelry is an incomparable experience. Within your box from us you will receive:<br\/>· Shopping Bag<br\/>· Jewelry Box<br\/>· Polishing Cloth<br\/>· Care Guide<br\/>· Return&Exchange Card<br\/>· Gemstone Certification(Moissanite Products)<br\/>· Free Silver Jewelry<br\/>· Silver Seal Bag<\/p>","text_font_size":"body-small","button_text":"","button_url":"","button_type":"btn--primary","button_size":"","button_style":"btn--solid","show_arrow":false,"image_aspect_ratio":1,"mobile_image_aspect_ratio":1,"heading_tag":"automatic"}},"image_TLXtjg":{"type":"image","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Beige_Purple_Minimalist_Fashion_Member_Benefits_Instagram_Post_e06c4002-4c89-47a3-9c64-18a15b3247ce.jpg","image_width":100,"image_shape":"normal","title":"How to get free jewelry","heading_font_size":"heading-medium","text":"<p><\/p><ul><li>Earn 1500 points→Amethyst&Lapis Lazuli<br\/><\/li><li>Earn 5500 points→Get a 0.3 carat real diamond Rings & $30 Off Instantly<\/li><li>Earn 12000 points→Get a 0.5 carat real diamond necklace & $35 Off Instantl<\/li><li>Earn 22000 points→Get a 1.0 carat real diamond ring & $40 Off Instantl<br\/><\/li><\/ul>","text_font_size":"body-small","button_text":"Learn more","button_url":"shopify:\/\/pages\/loyalty-program","button_type":"btn--primary","button_size":"","button_style":"btn--outline","show_arrow":false,"image_aspect_ratio":1,"mobile_image_aspect_ratio":1,"heading_tag":"automatic"}},"image_iWkdaF":{"type":"image","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/1174e8f1-969a-46bd-9f32-0e934347b33b_337b6594-f07d-4d01-a57f-7a5ff651df15.png","image_width":100,"image_shape":"normal","title":"Sterling Silver Jewelry-Free Gift！","heading_font_size":"heading-medium","text":"<p>Receive a free pearl necklace with every order! Whether you're a new or returning customer, enjoy a complimentary pearl necklace with every purchase.<\/p>","text_font_size":"body-small","button_text":"","button_url":"","button_type":"btn--primary","button_size":"","button_style":"btn--solid","show_arrow":false,"image_aspect_ratio":1,"mobile_image_aspect_ratio":1,"heading_tag":"automatic"}}},"block_order":["image_nU7PXt","image_TLXtjg","image_iWkdaF"],"settings":{"title":"","heading_font_size":"heading-medium","align_heading":"text-left","align_text":"text-left","width":"wrapper--full-padded","align_columns":"flex-align-top","layout":"grid","grid":3,"layout_mobile":"slider","color_scheme":"scheme-9c9f1fe6-23f9-471e-b2f3-03a31f5fb70d","padding_top":0,"padding_bottom":20,"heading_tag":"automatic"}},"section_accordion_group_aHpB9X":{"type":"section-accordion-group","blocks":{"heading_yg4GJP":{"type":"heading","settings":{"title":"Jewelry FAQs"}},"question_XQhW7B":{"type":"question","settings":{"default_open":false,"title":"What are your stones made of?","content":"<p>We use high-quality <a href=\"\/pages\/about-moissanite\" title=\"About Moissanite\"><em><strong>moissanite<\/strong><\/em><\/a> and <a href=\"\/pages\/about-cubic-zirconia\" title=\"About Cubic Zirconia\"><em><strong>5A cubic zirconia<\/strong><\/em><\/a>, both ethically and sustainably lab-created. These stones sparkle just as brilliantly as diamonds.<\/p>","show_icon":false,"icon_name":"icon-award","icon_size":20,"icon_color":"#545454"}},"question_qAAXCb":{"type":"question","settings":{"default_open":false,"title":"Will your jewelry turn my finger green?","content":"<p>No, it won’t! We can guarantee this.Our jewelry is made from 925 sterling silver plated with 18K gold, so it won’t discolor your skin, and it's hypoallergenic too.<\/p>","show_icon":false,"icon_name":"icon-award","icon_size":20,"icon_color":"#545454"}},"question_iNwfr6":{"type":"question","settings":{"default_open":false,"title":"How should I care for my jewelry?","content":"<p>When you’re not wearing it, store your jewelry in a jewelry box or pouch. A quick polish with a silver cloth will keep it shining. We recommend taking it off when showering, applying lotions, or during workouts to prevent oxidation. And while it's tempting, it's best not to wear it to bed!<\/p><p><a href=\"\/pages\/jewelry-care\" title=\"Jewelry care\"><em><strong>Jewelry Care Tips<\/strong><\/em><\/a><\/p>","show_icon":false,"icon_name":"icon-award","icon_size":20,"icon_color":"#545454"}},"question_xi9WAL":{"type":"question","settings":{"default_open":false,"title":"Do I get anything extra with my order?","content":"<p>Yes! Along with your jewelry and a gift box, you’ll receive a free surprise jewelry piece and a good luck <a href=\"\/pages\/mystery-box-promotion\" title=\"Mystery Box Promotion\"><em><strong>crystal<\/strong><\/em><\/a>. Plus, we <a href=\"\/pages\/planting-trees-together\" title=\"Planting Trees Together\"><em><strong>plant a tree<\/strong><\/em><\/a> in your name as part of our commitment to the planet.<\/p>","show_icon":false,"icon_name":"icon-award","icon_size":20,"icon_color":"#545454"}},"question_BqAf44":{"type":"question","settings":{"default_open":false,"title":"Can I customize my jewelry?","content":"<p>Yes, we offer <a href=\"\/pages\/custom-design\" title=\"Custom Design\"><em><strong>custom jewelry<\/strong><\/em><\/a>, and the design process is completely free! You can share any of your ideas with us, and we’ll bring them to life. Just reach out to us at service@solariijewelry.com, and we’ll make sure your vision becomes reality.<\/p>","show_icon":false,"icon_name":"icon-award","icon_size":20,"icon_color":"#545454"}},"question_tnt4BL":{"type":"question","settings":{"default_open":false,"title":"Have more questions?","content":"<p>We’ve highlighted the 5 most common questions here, but if you have more, feel free to check out our full <a href=\"\/pages\/faq\" title=\"FAQ\"><em><strong>FAQ<\/strong><\/em><\/a> section for additional details.<\/p>","show_icon":false,"icon_name":"icon-award","icon_size":20,"icon_color":"#545454"}}},"block_order":["heading_yg4GJP","question_XQhW7B","question_qAAXCb","question_iNwfr6","question_xi9WAL","question_BqAf44","question_tnt4BL"],"disabled":true,"settings":{"heading_font_size":"heading-medium","question_font_size":"heading-small","width":"wrapper--narrow","columns":"1","color_scheme":"","padding_top":50,"padding_bottom":50}},"section_rich_text_4DqYi8":{"type":"section-rich-text","blocks":{"heading_rNXgW7":{"type":"heading","settings":{"title":"SAME APPEARANCE MORE BRILLIANCE","heading_font_size":"heading-medium","padding_bottom":6,"heading_tag":"automatic"}}},"block_order":["heading_rNXgW7"],"name":"Rich text","s